Revelation Church Of Jesus Christ (RCJC) aka Revelation Church LA has unveiled plans for her first ever Easter program since moving into their new home. It will be the first passion week program that will be held in their new headquarters. The Good Friday service will be held on April 2, 2021, at 7:30 PM. The service was announced in church after Palm Sunday service which officially kicked off passion week for all Christians, There will also be a special Easter Sunday service on April 4, 2021, at 10:00 AM. Revelation Church Of Jesus Christ (RCJC) aka Revelation Church LA was founded in 2013 by Prophet Lovy Elias as a Bible study group, but began to operate officially as a non profit organization formally known as The Revelation Church of Jesus Christ in 2017. It has since continued to grow with over 400 dedicated members in Los Angeles and hundreds of thousands more who join weekly church services virtually worldwide. Revelation Church LA is Located at 580 E Easy St Simi Valley, CA and holds prophetic service every Thursday from 7:30pm-11pm and Sunday service at 10am. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that
